s a bombardment history similar to that of Triton over one more\nsimilar to that of the Galilean satellites.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Mar 2020 18:00:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 18 Dec 2020 14:30:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-06"}
