S survey is quite sensitive to the\ndiffuse Galactic synchrotron radiation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Mar 2020 18:00:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 20 Mar 2020 13:34:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-13"}
