ization has a\nmaximum value at a wavelength ($\\lambda_{\\rm max}$) of $440 \\pm 110$ nm,\nconsistent with values found for other nearby stars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Mar 2020 23:23:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-01"}
