f two kinds of\nemitting areas implies that the one-zone model is unsuitable to reproduce, at\nleast a part of the observed SEDs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Mar 2020 02:20:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-27"}
