yscapes and SYNTHIA to\nCityscapes, and achieve the new state-of-the-art segmentation accuracy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Mar 2020 04:43:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 22 Apr 2020 04:25:09 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 9 Jun 2020 17:56:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-11"}
