y of bulk-disclination correspondence\nunveils a novel fundamental phenomenon and a new paradigm for exploring\ntopological materials.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Mar 2020 10:41:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 20 Mar 2020 22:30:45 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 14 Sep 2020 03:23:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-26"}
