rise of objectivity in the\nquantum-to-classical transition.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Mar 2020 11:05:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 6 Oct 2020 15:40:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-07"}
