mation bias by analyzers and pin down\npossible tuning of the specific EFT implementations. Both independent teams\nhave recovered the true values of the input parameters within sub-percent\nstatistical errors corresponding to the total simulation volume.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Mar 2020 15:35:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 10 Dec 2020 02:36:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-04"}
